      - title: Menu Text
        value: 
        type: 0
        typeString: 
      - title: Dialogue Text
        value: 'While it is stil sad to your friends and loved ones that you are
          dead, I am glad to hear you are not afraid.

          Do not worry, everything
          will be alright.'
